{code}
# euca-modify-property -pbootstrap.tx.concurrent_update_retries=25
{code}

Ingress/egress rule changes are retried and that setting controls the default number of retries. Due to the structure of the CloudFormation template there can be many attempts to concurrently update the security group, meaning a large number of retries is necessary.

There is no correct value for retries, it depends on the templates in use, but we may want to update the default number of retries for security group rule updates and make that a separately configurable cloud property if users run into this issue.

